  <div class="content">
  








  <strong>First Sentence:</strong><br />



As I got off the plane, he was waiting for me, holding up a scrap of cardboard with my name scribbled on it.&nbsp;<a href="/gp/reader/0345409469?ie=UTF8&amp;p=S00K&amp;checkSum=nQFluM8kyRaywgmqshJALBGnfdR9un%2B33zApA81XcHA%3D#reader-link" onclick="if (typeof(SitbReader) != 'undefined') { SitbReader.LightboxActions.openReaderToPage(20, 'nQFluM8kyRaywgmqshJALBGnfdR9un+33zApA81XcHA=', 'sib_fs_bod'); return false; }">Read the first page</a>

  <div class="spacer"></div>


  






